title: FC Čechie Uhříněves
text: FC Čechie Uhříněves is a <a href="association%20football">football</a> club located in <a href="Prague">Prague</a>-<a href="Uh%C5%99%C3%ADn%C4%9Bves">Uhříněves</a>, <a href="Czech%20Republic">Czech Republic</a>. It currently plays in the I.A třída skupina A – Praha, which is in the sixth tier of the <a href="Czech%20Republic%20football%20league%20system">Czech football system</a>. The club took part in the first round of the <a href="2012%E2%80%9313%20Czech%20Cup">2012–13 Czech Cup</a>.
